# Copy this file to .env.local and fill in your values.
# .env.local is gitignored and never committed.
#
# UDCPINE_BOOTSTRAP_TOKEN
#   Sets a stable, reusable bootstrap token for the backend's pairing URL.
#   When this is set, the printed "Pair a device" URL stays the same across
#   server restarts — a requirement for the Pi kiosk, which is hard-coded to
#   a single URL at deploy time (see plans/ops/2026-05-27-pi-boot-to-kiosk.md).
#
#   Without this var, a fresh random token is generated on every server start,
#   which means the kiosk URL changes on every `make serve` and the Pi can no
#   longer auto-pair after a laptop reboot.
#
#   Generate a token:
#     openssl rand -hex 32
#
# UDCPINE_BOOTSTRAP_TOKEN=your-stable-token-here
